# 🚀 Day 32: Cloud Security – Identity, Access Management (IAM) & Monitoring

## 🔐 Topics Covered
- Cloud Security Fundamentals
- IAM (Identity and Access Management):
  - Least Privilege, MFA, RBAC
  - AWS IAM, Azure AD, GCP IAM structure
  - IAM Misconfigurations and Attack Vectors
  - Monitoring in the Cloud:
  - AWS CloudTrail, Azure Monitor, GCP Logs
  - Importance of alerting, audit trails, log retention

